CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 14, 1950, pg. 5, reads: "Teen-Agers Party - The Schenley Heights Teen-Agers held a very gay formal party recently at the Centre Avenue YWCA. Among those present were the above lovelies.  Left to right:  Delores Parker, Geraldine Williams, Jean Randall, Phyllis Harper, Menora Covenia and Nancy Foster.  Seated on the floor are Wilma Duncan and Barbara Griggs. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of "Schenley Heights Teen-Agers," including from left: Menora Covenia, Barbara Griggs, Phyllis Harper, Geraldine Williams, Delores Parker, Nancy Foster, two unknown women, Jean Randall, and Wilma Duncan in center rear, posed in front of Christmas tree in YMCA or YWCA
